            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "194cca6642c8_15",
          "href": null,
          "name": "c9c2",
          "text": "You can get involved by joining any or all of these efforts. The important thing is that local people are doing things that can be networked to achieve global goals. Consider the “donut” economics framework. When we begin to see how different nations fail to achieve social goals while over-consuming the rest of nature, it becomes possible to focus our attention on these deficits.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 206,
              "href": "https://www.kateraworth.com/doughnut/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 179,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 206,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 179,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "194cca6642c8_16",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1511",
          "text": "We can compare the blue areas (social metrics) with green areas (environmental metrics) to see if a country is sustainable. Learn more here.",
          "metadata": {
            "id": "0*gGTH5NQnppB_cNzi.jpg",
            "alt": null
          },
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": "INSET_CENTER",
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 139,
              "href": "https://goodlife.leeds.ac.uk/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 135,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "IMG"
        },
        {
          "id": "194cca6642c8_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "5ea9",
          "text": "One way to regenerate our planet is to first regenerate the local ecosystems of local places. Then we measure our progress toward national targets of health and resilience as we coordinate across regions to move toward planetary health outcomes. Sounds easy in principle, but this is really going to be hard. In fact it is probably the most difficult thing humans have ever done!",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 93,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "194cca6642c8_18",
          "href": null,
          "name": "d428",
          "text": "So we’d better get started. For my part, I am offering a series of workshops on regenerative design to help bring greater coherence to existing networks. You can join any of the projects above (or start your own!) and weave a tapestry of regeneration for the thriving of future generations.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 99,
              "href": "https://mailchi.mp/4335bc3f2170/we-have-three-upcoming-workshops?",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 55,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 99,
